{
  "book": "1nephi",
  "bookName": "1 Nephi",
  "chapter": 15,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "ddDFRErfhdc2asyySOG5",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "Samuel"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 547.886,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 5.294,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that after I, Nephi, had been carried away in the Spirit,",
      "verse": "15:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 5.474,
      "end": 7.285,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and seen all these things,",
      "verse": "15:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 7.465,
      "end": 9.833,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I returned to the tent of my father.",
      "verse": "15:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 10.513,
      "end": 13.207,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I beheld my brethren,",
      "verse": "15:2",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 13.387,
      "end": 15.709,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they were disputing one with another",
      "verse": "15:2",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 15.889,
      "end": 19.372,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "concerning the things which my father had spoken unto them.",
      "verse": "15:2",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 20.052,
      "end": 23.256,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For he truly spake many great things unto them,",
      "verse": "15:3",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 23.436,
      "end": 25.572,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which were hard to be understood,",
      "verse": "15:3",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 25.752,
      "end": 28.167,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "save a man should inquire of the Lord;",
      "verse": "15:3",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 28.347,
      "end": 30.437,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they being hard in their hearts,",
      "verse": "15:3",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 30.617,
      "end": 33.775,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "therefore they did not look unto the Lord as they ought.",
      "verse": "15:3",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 34.455,
      "end": 36.963,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now I, Nephi, was grieved",
      "verse": "15:4",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 37.143,
      "end": 39.697,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of the hardness of their hearts,",
      "verse": "15:4",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 39.877,
      "end": 42.988,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also, because of the things which I had seen,",
      "verse": "15:4",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 43.168,
      "end": 45.862,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and knew they must unavoidably come to pass",
      "verse": "15:4",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 46.042,
      "end": 49.571,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of the great wickedness of the children of men.",
      "verse": "15:4",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 50.251,
      "end": 53.966,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I was overcome because of my afflictions,",
      "verse": "15:5",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 54.146,
      "end": 57.954,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for I considered that mine afflictions were great above all,",
      "verse": "15:5",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 58.134,
      "end": 60.502,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of the destruction of my people,",
      "verse": "15:5",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 60.682,
      "end": 62.911,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for I had beheld their fall.",
      "verse": "15:5",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 63.591,
      "end": 66.749,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that after I had received strength",
      "verse": "15:6",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 66.929,
      "end": 68.787,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I spake unto my brethren,",
      "verse": "15:6",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 68.967,
      "end": 72.357,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "desiring to know of them the cause of their disputations.",
      "verse": "15:6",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 73.037,
      "end": 78.842,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And they said: Behold, we cannot understand the words which our father hath spoken",
      "verse": "15:7",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 79.022,
      "end": 82.366,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "concerning the natural branches of the olive tree,",
      "verse": "15:7",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 82.546,
      "end": 84.914,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also concerning the Gentiles.",
      "verse": "15:7",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 85.594,
      "end": 87.173,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I said unto them:",
      "verse": "15:8",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 87.353,
      "end": 89.118,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Have ye inquired of the Lord?",
      "verse": "15:8",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 89.798,
      "end": 91.423,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And they said unto me:",
      "verse": "15:9",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 91.603,
      "end": 93.089,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "We have not;",
      "verse": "15:9",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 93.269,
      "end": 96.241,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for the Lord maketh no such thing known unto us.",
      "verse": "15:9",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 96.921,
      "end": 98.593,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, I said unto them:",
      "verse": "15:10",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 98.773,
      "end": 102.163,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "How is it that ye do not keep the commandments of the Lord?",
      "verse": "15:10",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 102.343,
      "end": 104.293,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "How is it that ye will perish,",
      "verse": "15:10",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 104.473,
      "end": 106.795,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of the hardness of your hearts?",
      "verse": "15:10",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 107.475,
      "end": 110.447,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Do ye not remember the things which the Lord hath said?\u2014",
      "verse": "15:11",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 110.627,
      "end": 113.831,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "If ye will not harden your hearts, and ask me in faith,",
      "verse": "15:11",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 114.011,
      "end": 116.147,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "believing that ye shall receive,",
      "verse": "15:11",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 116.327,
      "end": 118.928,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "with diligence in keeping my commandments,",
      "verse": "15:11",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 119.108,
      "end": 121.987,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "surely these things shall be made known unto you.",
      "verse": "15:11",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 122.667,
      "end": 124.385,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, I say unto you,",
      "verse": "15:12",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 124.565,
      "end": 127.862,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the house of Israel was compared unto an olive tree",
      "verse": "15:12",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 128.042,
      "end": 129.853,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "by the Spirit of the Lord",
      "verse": "15:12",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 130.033,
      "end": 131.751,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which was in our father;",
      "verse": "15:12",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 131.931,
      "end": 135.507,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and behold are we not broken off from the house of Israel,",
      "verse": "15:12",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 135.687,
      "end": 138.241,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and are we not a branch of the house of Israel?",
      "verse": "15:12",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 138.921,
      "end": 141.754,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now, the thing which our father meaneth",
      "verse": "15:13",
      "lineIndex": 49
    },
    {
      "start": 141.934,
      "end": 145.649,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "concerning the grafting in of the natural branches",
      "verse": "15:13",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 145.829,
      "end": 148.058,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "through the fulness of the Gentiles, is,",
      "verse": "15:13",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 148.238,
      "end": 149.863,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that in the latter days,",
      "verse": "15:13",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 150.043,
      "end": 152.969,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "when our seed shall have dwindled in unbelief,",
      "verse": "15:13",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 153.149,
      "end": 156.353,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, for the space of many years, and many generations",
      "verse": "15:13",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 156.533,
      "end": 161.084,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "after the Messiah shall be manifested in body unto the children of men,",
      "verse": "15:13",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 161.264,
      "end": 166.326,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "then shall the fulness of the gospel of the Messiah come unto the Gentiles,",
      "verse": "15:13",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 166.506,
      "end": 169.989,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and from the Gentiles unto the remnant of our seed\u2014",
      "verse": "15:13",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 170.669,
      "end": 172.016,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And at that day",
      "verse": "15:14",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 172.196,
      "end": 174.89,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "shall the remnant of our seed know",
      "verse": "15:14",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 175.07,
      "end": 177.624,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they are of the house of Israel,",
      "verse": "15:14",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 177.804,
      "end": 180.962,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and that they are the covenant people of the Lord;",
      "verse": "15:14",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 181.142,
      "end": 182.767,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and then shall they know",
      "verse": "15:14",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 182.947,
      "end": 185.733,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and come to the knowledge of their forefathers,",
      "verse": "15:14",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 185.913,
      "end": 189.257,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also to the knowledge of the gospel of their Redeemer,",
      "verse": "15:14",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 189.437,
      "end": 192.641,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which was ministered unto their fathers by him;",
      "verse": "15:14",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 192.821,
      "end": 196.304,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, they shall come to the knowledge of their Redeemer",
      "verse": "15:14",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 196.484,
      "end": 198.667,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the very points of his doctrine,",
      "verse": "15:14",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 198.847,
      "end": 202.284,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they may know how to come unto him and be saved.",
      "verse": "15:14",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 202.964,
      "end": 205.24,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then at that day will they not rejoice",
      "verse": "15:15",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 205.42,
      "end": 208.253,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and give praise unto their everlasting God,",
      "verse": "15:15",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 208.433,
      "end": 210.569,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "their rock and their salvation?",
      "verse": "15:15",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 210.749,
      "end": 212.421,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea, at that day,",
      "verse": "15:15",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 212.601,
      "end": 217.059,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "will they not receive the strength and nourishment from the true vine?",
      "verse": "15:15",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 217.239,
      "end": 220.165,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea, will they not come unto the true fold of God?",
      "verse": "15:15",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 220.845,
      "end": 222.563,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, I say unto you,",
      "verse": "15:16",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 222.743,
      "end": 226.551,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea; they shall be remembered again among the house of Israel;",
      "verse": "15:16",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 226.731,
      "end": 228.449,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they shall be grafted in,",
      "verse": "15:16",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 228.629,
      "end": 233.041,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "being a natural branch of the olive tree, into the true olive tree.",
      "verse": "15:16",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 233.721,
      "end": 235.857,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And this is what our father meaneth;",
      "verse": "15:17",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 236.037,
      "end": 238.545,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he meaneth that it will not come to pass",
      "verse": "15:17",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 238.725,
      "end": 241.465,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "until after they are scattered by the Gentiles;",
      "verse": "15:17",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 241.645,
      "end": 245.5,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he meaneth that it shall come by way of the Gentiles,",
      "verse": "15:17",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 245.68,
      "end": 248.791,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the Lord may show his power unto the Gentiles,",
      "verse": "15:17",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 248.971,
      "end": 252.64,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for the very cause that he shall be rejected of the Jews,",
      "verse": "15:17",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 252.82,
      "end": 254.353,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "or of the house of Israel.",
      "verse": "15:17",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 255.033,
      "end": 258.377,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, our father hath not spoken of our seed alone,",
      "verse": "15:18",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 258.557,
      "end": 262.644,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but also of all the house of Israel, pointing to the covenant",
      "verse": "15:18",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 262.824,
      "end": 265.61,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which should be fulfilled in the latter days;",
      "verse": "15:18",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 265.79,
      "end": 269.366,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which covenant the Lord made to our father Abraham, saying:",
      "verse": "15:18",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 269.546,
      "end": 272.936,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "In thy seed shall all the kindreds of the earth be blessed.",
      "verse": "15:18",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 273.616,
      "end": 278.446,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I, Nephi, spake much unto them concerning these things;",
      "verse": "15:19",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 278.626,
      "end": 280.344,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, I spake unto them",
      "verse": "15:19",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 280.524,
      "end": 284.053,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "concerning the restoration of the Jews in the latter days.",
      "verse": "15:19",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 284.733,
      "end": 286.683,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I did rehearse unto them",
      "verse": "15:20",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 286.863,
      "end": 288.628,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the words of Isaiah,",
      "verse": "15:20",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 288.808,
      "end": 292.198,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who spake concerning the restoration of the Jews,",
      "verse": "15:20",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 292.378,
      "end": 294.514,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "or of the house of Israel;",
      "verse": "15:20",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 294.694,
      "end": 296.691,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and after they were restored",
      "verse": "15:20",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 296.871,
      "end": 299.007,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they should no more be confounded,",
      "verse": "15:20",
      "lineIndex": 99
    },
    {
      "start": 299.187,
      "end": 301.323,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "neither should they be scattered again.",
      "verse": "15:20",
      "lineIndex": 100
    },
    {
      "start": 301.503,
      "end": 306.193,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I did speak many words unto my brethren,",
      "verse": "15:20",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 306.373,
      "end": 307.859,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they were pacified",
      "verse": "15:20",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 308.039,
      "end": 310.407,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and did humble themselves before the Lord.",
      "verse": "15:20",
      "lineIndex": 103
    },
    {
      "start": 311.087,
      "end": 315.22,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that they did speak unto me again, saying:",
      "verse": "15:21",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 315.4,
      "end": 318.976,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "What meaneth this thing which our father saw in a dream?",
      "verse": "15:21",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 319.156,
      "end": 321.199,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "What meaneth the tree which he saw?",
      "verse": "15:21",
      "lineIndex": 107
    },
    {
      "start": 321.879,
      "end": 323.458,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I said unto them:",
      "verse": "15:22",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 323.638,
      "end": 326.285,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "It was a representation of the tree of life.",
      "verse": "15:22",
      "lineIndex": 109
    },
    {
      "start": 326.965,
      "end": 328.59,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And they said unto me:",
      "verse": "15:23",
      "lineIndex": 110
    },
    {
      "start": 328.77,
      "end": 332.253,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "What meaneth the rod of iron which our father saw,",
      "verse": "15:23",
      "lineIndex": 111
    },
    {
      "start": 332.433,
      "end": 333.966,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that led to the tree?",
      "verse": "15:23",
      "lineIndex": 112
    },
    {
      "start": 334.646,
      "end": 337.432,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I said unto them that it was the word of God;",
      "verse": "15:24",
      "lineIndex": 113
    },
    {
      "start": 337.612,
      "end": 340.723,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and whoso would hearken unto the word of God,",
      "verse": "15:24",
      "lineIndex": 114
    },
    {
      "start": 340.903,
      "end": 342.946,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and would hold fast unto it,",
      "verse": "15:24",
      "lineIndex": 115
    },
    {
      "start": 343.126,
      "end": 344.891,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they would never perish;",
      "verse": "15:24",
      "lineIndex": 116
    },
    {
      "start": 345.071,
      "end": 347.347,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "neither could the temptations",
      "verse": "15:24",
      "lineIndex": 117
    },
    {
      "start": 347.527,
      "end": 350.313,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the fiery darts of the adversary",
      "verse": "15:24",
      "lineIndex": 118
    },
    {
      "start": 350.493,
      "end": 352.815,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "overpower them unto blindness,",
      "verse": "15:24",
      "lineIndex": 119
    },
    {
      "start": 352.995,
      "end": 355.363,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to lead them away to destruction.",
      "verse": "15:24",
      "lineIndex": 120
    },
    {
      "start": 356.043,
      "end": 358.551,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, I, Nephi, did exhort them",
      "verse": "15:25",
      "lineIndex": 121
    },
    {
      "start": 358.731,
      "end": 361.192,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to give heed unto the word of the Lord;",
      "verse": "15:25",
      "lineIndex": 122
    },
    {
      "start": 361.372,
      "end": 364.809,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, I did exhort them with all the energies of my soul,",
      "verse": "15:25",
      "lineIndex": 123
    },
    {
      "start": 364.989,
      "end": 367.59,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and with all the faculty which I possessed,",
      "verse": "15:25",
      "lineIndex": 124
    },
    {
      "start": 367.77,
      "end": 370.603,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they would give heed to the word of God",
      "verse": "15:25",
      "lineIndex": 125
    },
    {
      "start": 370.783,
      "end": 374.312,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and remember to keep his commandments always in all things.",
      "verse": "15:25",
      "lineIndex": 126
    },
    {
      "start": 374.992,
      "end": 376.617,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And they said unto me:",
      "verse": "15:26",
      "lineIndex": 127
    },
    {
      "start": 376.797,
      "end": 379.955,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "What meaneth the river of water which our father saw?",
      "verse": "15:26",
      "lineIndex": 128
    },
    {
      "start": 380.635,
      "end": 382.307,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I said unto them",
      "verse": "15:27",
      "lineIndex": 129
    },
    {
      "start": 382.487,
      "end": 385.598,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the water which my father saw was filthiness;",
      "verse": "15:27",
      "lineIndex": 130
    },
    {
      "start": 385.778,
      "end": 388.936,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and so much was his mind swallowed up in other things",
      "verse": "15:27",
      "lineIndex": 131
    },
    {
      "start": 389.116,
      "end": 392.506,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he beheld not the filthiness of the water.",
      "verse": "15:27",
      "lineIndex": 132
    },
    {
      "start": 393.186,
      "end": 396.437,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I said unto them that it was an awful gulf,",
      "verse": "15:28",
      "lineIndex": 133
    },
    {
      "start": 396.617,
      "end": 398.521,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which separated the wicked",
      "verse": "15:28",
      "lineIndex": 134
    },
    {
      "start": 398.701,
      "end": 400.373,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "from the tree of life,",
      "verse": "15:28",
      "lineIndex": 135
    },
    {
      "start": 400.553,
      "end": 402.503,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also from the saints of God.",
      "verse": "15:28",
      "lineIndex": 136
    },
    {
      "start": 403.183,
      "end": 404.855,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I said unto them",
      "verse": "15:29",
      "lineIndex": 137
    },
    {
      "start": 405.035,
      "end": 408.239,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that it was a representation of that awful hell,",
      "verse": "15:29",
      "lineIndex": 138
    },
    {
      "start": 408.419,
      "end": 411.995,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which the angel said unto me was prepared for the wicked.",
      "verse": "15:29",
      "lineIndex": 139
    },
    {
      "start": 412.675,
      "end": 415.601,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I said unto them that our father also saw",
      "verse": "15:30",
      "lineIndex": 140
    },
    {
      "start": 415.781,
      "end": 419.914,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the justice of God did also divide the wicked from the righteous;",
      "verse": "15:30",
      "lineIndex": 141
    },
    {
      "start": 420.094,
      "end": 422.137,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the brightness thereof",
      "verse": "15:30",
      "lineIndex": 142
    },
    {
      "start": 422.317,
      "end": 425.382,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "was like unto the brightness of a flaming fire,",
      "verse": "15:30",
      "lineIndex": 143
    },
    {
      "start": 425.562,
      "end": 428.813,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which ascendeth up unto God forever and ever,",
      "verse": "15:30",
      "lineIndex": 144
    },
    {
      "start": 428.993,
      "end": 430.479,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and hath no end.",
      "verse": "15:30",
      "lineIndex": 145
    },
    {
      "start": 431.159,
      "end": 432.784,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And they said unto me:",
      "verse": "15:31",
      "lineIndex": 147
    },
    {
      "start": 432.964,
      "end": 437.144,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Doth this thing mean the torment of the body in the days of probation,",
      "verse": "15:31",
      "lineIndex": 148
    },
    {
      "start": 437.324,
      "end": 440.064,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "or doth it mean the final state of the soul",
      "verse": "15:31",
      "lineIndex": 149
    },
    {
      "start": 440.244,
      "end": 442.566,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "after the death of the temporal body,",
      "verse": "15:31",
      "lineIndex": 150
    },
    {
      "start": 442.746,
      "end": 445.904,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "or doth it speak of the things which are temporal?",
      "verse": "15:31",
      "lineIndex": 151
    },
    {
      "start": 446.584,
      "end": 448.952,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I said unto them",
      "verse": "15:32",
      "lineIndex": 152
    },
    {
      "start": 449.132,
      "end": 453.683,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that it was a representation of things both temporal and spiritual;",
      "verse": "15:32",
      "lineIndex": 153
    },
    {
      "start": 453.863,
      "end": 457.578,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for the day should come that they must be judged of their works,",
      "verse": "15:32",
      "lineIndex": 154
    },
    {
      "start": 457.758,
      "end": 462.959,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even the works which were done by the temporal body in their days of probation.",
      "verse": "15:32",
      "lineIndex": 155
    },
    {
      "start": 463.639,
      "end": 466.704,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, if they should die in their wickedness",
      "verse": "15:33",
      "lineIndex": 156
    },
    {
      "start": 466.884,
      "end": 468.788,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they must be cast off also,",
      "verse": "15:33",
      "lineIndex": 157
    },
    {
      "start": 468.968,
      "end": 471.429,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "as to the things which are spiritual,",
      "verse": "15:33",
      "lineIndex": 158
    },
    {
      "start": 471.609,
      "end": 473.885,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which are pertaining to righteousness;",
      "verse": "15:33",
      "lineIndex": 159
    },
    {
      "start": 474.065,
      "end": 477.269,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, they must be brought to stand before God,",
      "verse": "15:33",
      "lineIndex": 160
    },
    {
      "start": 477.449,
      "end": 479.539,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to be judged of their works;",
      "verse": "15:33",
      "lineIndex": 161
    },
    {
      "start": 479.719,
      "end": 484.177,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and if their works have been filthiness they must needs be filthy;",
      "verse": "15:33",
      "lineIndex": 162
    },
    {
      "start": 484.357,
      "end": 486.958,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and if they be filthy it must needs be",
      "verse": "15:33",
      "lineIndex": 163
    },
    {
      "start": 487.138,
      "end": 490.11,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they cannot dwell in the kingdom of God;",
      "verse": "15:33",
      "lineIndex": 164
    },
    {
      "start": 490.29,
      "end": 493.216,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "if so, the kingdom of God must be filthy also.",
      "verse": "15:33",
      "lineIndex": 165
    },
    {
      "start": 493.896,
      "end": 495.893,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But behold, I say unto you,",
      "verse": "15:34",
      "lineIndex": 166
    },
    {
      "start": 496.073,
      "end": 498.395,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the kingdom of God is not filthy,",
      "verse": "15:34",
      "lineIndex": 167
    },
    {
      "start": 498.575,
      "end": 501.083,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and there cannot any unclean thing",
      "verse": "15:34",
      "lineIndex": 168
    },
    {
      "start": 501.263,
      "end": 503.446,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "enter into the kingdom of God;",
      "verse": "15:34",
      "lineIndex": 169
    },
    {
      "start": 503.626,
      "end": 507.063,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore there must needs be a place of filthiness",
      "verse": "15:34",
      "lineIndex": 170
    },
    {
      "start": 507.243,
      "end": 509.611,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "prepared for that which is filthy.",
      "verse": "15:34",
      "lineIndex": 171
    },
    {
      "start": 510.291,
      "end": 512.334,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And there is a place prepared,",
      "verse": "15:35",
      "lineIndex": 172
    },
    {
      "start": 512.514,
      "end": 515.951,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even that awful hell of which I have spoken,",
      "verse": "15:35",
      "lineIndex": 173
    },
    {
      "start": 516.131,
      "end": 518.639,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the devil is the preparator of it;",
      "verse": "15:35",
      "lineIndex": 174
    },
    {
      "start": 518.819,
      "end": 521.698,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore the final state of the souls of men",
      "verse": "15:35",
      "lineIndex": 175
    },
    {
      "start": 521.878,
      "end": 525.407,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "is to dwell in the kingdom of God, or to be cast out",
      "verse": "15:35",
      "lineIndex": 176
    },
    {
      "start": 525.587,
      "end": 528.188,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of that justice of which I have spoken.",
      "verse": "15:35",
      "lineIndex": 177
    },
    {
      "start": 528.868,
      "end": 532.258,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, the wicked are rejected from the righteous,",
      "verse": "15:36",
      "lineIndex": 178
    },
    {
      "start": 532.438,
      "end": 534.853,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also from that tree of life,",
      "verse": "15:36",
      "lineIndex": 179
    },
    {
      "start": 535.033,
      "end": 537.169,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "whose fruit is most precious",
      "verse": "15:36",
      "lineIndex": 180
    },
    {
      "start": 537.349,
      "end": 539.996,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and most desirable above all other fruits;",
      "verse": "15:36",
      "lineIndex": 181
    },
    {
      "start": 540.176,
      "end": 543.659,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, and it is the greatest of all the gifts of God.",
      "verse": "15:36",
      "lineIndex": 182
    },
    {
      "start": 543.839,
      "end": 546.207,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And thus I spake unto my brethren.",
      "verse": "15:36",
      "lineIndex": 183
    },
    {
      "start": 546.387,
      "end": 547.223,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Amen.",
      "verse": "15:36",
      "lineIndex": 184
    }
  ]
}